{"tid":2337665,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"講下自己讀書/睇戲有咩惡趣味","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T09:40:13.000Z","uid":173852,"like":3,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a3318593fae279776bbc8493e57533dc3baf536a","tid":2337665,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"惡趣﹐簡而言之﹐即係明知唔太合理﹐唔太主流﹐但都無辦法就係好依味既事<br />\n等小弟先拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n影視/漫畫方面:<br />\n<br />\n1.覺得張家輝同王家衛一樣咁正<br />\n<br />\n2.中意浪漫愛情喜劇/少女漫畫﹐就算明知係爛片都覺得好睇﹐雖然唔會重睇。<br />\n(好似《莎翁情史》﹐根本係名過其實既垃圾﹐但睇落又幾enjoy)<br />\n<br />\n3.中意大團圓結局﹐好似老人家中意食糖咁。<br />\n<br />\n4.好撚憎市面9成「人性黑暗」既題材﹐覺得只拎一面有幾大發幾大相當戇鳩。<br />\n<br />\n5.中意港漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.覺得TVB而家既劇唔差<br />\n<br />\n7.覺得D人屌歷史劇邊part邊part唔合歷史相當戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n8.覺得80,90年代班傻鳩文化人屌通俗文化唔夠高大上相當戇鳩﹐依家又咪追住黎含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係以上依幾點我應該都做唔成文青 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f419d3eecd80924b751513f007fb59b1f95e15e9","tid":2337665,"uid":131617,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"你係唔係仲好鍾意駁嘴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca02b1834e9b757b19d7f6bc28cf2eb3047b8b43","tid":2337665,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"高大上<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b88280fbd86b209f952005f0379ae612d24c83c","tid":2337665,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"